{"tid":2289703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★日本網購騙局買 PS5 變 PS4","createTime":"2020-11-17T12:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T16:18:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"134644319a0ceada5a137aae9d9dffdfa0171385","tid":2289703,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:22:41.000Z","msg":"PlayStation 5 (PS5)  於上個星期在日本推出後，不少人都搶購，以及炒價賺錢。有日本網民原本以為能以較便宜的價格網購 PS5 ，但是打開包裝卻發現是 PS4，大為失望。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n有日本網民在網上分享，表示自己原本想在網上購買 PS5，當見到有商品雖然價格 6 萬日元（約港幣 HK$4434）,較 PS5 原價貴，但是與其他炒價相比，仍很划算，於是他就選擇購買，但是當他收到 PS5，並打開包裝時，卻發現是 PS4，他再次察看網頁內容的時候，才知道網頁其實有寫明 PS5 盒裝 PS4，另外不設退換，其後他很後悔自己當時沒有看清商品內容，於是出帖提醒其他網民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/11/17/ps5-ps4-japan/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F11%2F17%2Fps5-ps4-japan%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4wogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=7fb9e3d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/11/17/ps5-ps4-japan/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"c6c073cadd19ed6fa3027663fb243fefaf01d685","tid":2289703,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:26:52.000Z","msg":"父親因買錯PSP被毆打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0121a70351049b03ab2d73bf3f38c93a88cadad6","tid":2289703,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b3b3e4606e87b47e48d008752fc1cb76cbf027","tid":2289703,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:36:52.000Z","msg":"重點係商品標題寫咩先？如果寫PS5咁分明誤導啦"},{"pid":"7a2d6d3aa7fc024ff99297d8e3227fde5178baf1","tid":2289703,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:53:49.000Z","msg":"諗起當年有人買Diablo 3收到3粒菠蘿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif